  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b8e\u0bb4\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bc2\u0bb2 \u0b89\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bc7\u0bb5\u0bc8 ; \u0b95\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bc8 - \u0b9a\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bb8\u0bcd, \u0b9a\u0b9c\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A written confirmation is required; Condition of alliance - Dulles, Sajith rushes to Sampandan's residence",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is known that the Tamil National Federation has decided that a written commitment should be given to support Dulles Alagaperuma, who was proposed as a presidential candidate, and it has also decided to call them in person and request them.",
        "As the voting for the election of the new interim president is going to be held tomorrow, the meeting of the Tamil National Federation started today at 5.30 pm at Sambandan's residence in Colombo to take a final decision on who to support.",
        "During this, it is said that there were various debates among the federation representatives and party leaders about what are the advantages and disadvantages for Tamils \u200b\u200bin supporting Dulles Alagaperuma and also what are the consequences of supporting Ranil Wickramasinghe.",
        "Also, it appears that the representatives focused on rejecting the referendum by not supporting both of them. However, reports also say that several representatives who participated in the meeting insisted that if Dulles is going to support the beauty, a written confirmation should be obtained from her.",
        "In particular, the representatives have emphasized that time-bound commitment is necessary regarding issues that cannot be resolved immediately, including the release of political prisoners and occupation issues.",
        "Following this, Federation President Sampanthan has invited presidential candidate Dalus Alagaperuma and opposition leader Sajith Premadasa to come to his residence in person.",
        "In this case, there are confirmed reports that Dallas and Sajith will go to Sampanthan's house shortly and the delegation led by Sampanthan, the president of the federation, is currently waiting to meet them."
      ],
